{
  "chapter": 36,
  "chapter_summary": "陆小凤与方玉飞在银钩赌坊相遇，陆小凤被一位冰山般的美女冷若霜吸引。冷若霜故作冷淡后引诱陆小凤前往秘密的金钩赌坊，要求蒙住他的眼睛。到达后陆小凤发现被困在一间四面铁板的密室中，酒坛迷烟将他迷晕。醒来后他发现自己被栽赃八件大案，杨捕头带人抓捕。三个来自九天十地组织的绿袍老人出现，声称陆小凤杀了教主之子，要他偿命。陆小凤以一心二用的奇招夺刀剑反击后逃脱。他回到银钩赌坊调查，用赌计骗过打手大牛和瞎子进入赌场，在墙上一幅拙劣山水画后发现暗门，进入地下密室，遇见另一个冷若冰霜的神秘女子。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_jing",
      "speaker_name": "赌精",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两个自命不凡的年轻人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_jing",
      "speaker_name": "赌精",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "穿银缎子衣裳的一个，就是这赌坊大老板的小舅子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "有人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说他就是蓝胡子那新夫人的弟弟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_jing",
      "speaker_name": "赌精",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嫡亲的弟弟！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "有人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他是不是叫做'银鹞子'方玉飞？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_jing",
      "speaker_name": "赌精",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "有人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听说他本来就是个很有名的花花公子，吃喝嫖赌，样样精通，轻功也很不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_jing",
      "speaker_name": "赌精",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以还有很多人说他是个采花盗！其实他想要女人，用手指勾一勾就来了，根本用不着半夜去采花。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "有人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听说他姐姐方玉香也是个很有名的美人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "有人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "比花花解语，比玉玉生香。那女人又岂是'美人'两个字所能形容的，简直是个倾国倾城的尤物！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "有人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方玉飞旁边那小子又是谁？怎么长着两撇和眉毛一模一样的胡子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "有人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "假如我没有猜错，他一定就是那个长着四条眉毛的陆小凤！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "方玉飞",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这屋子里好看的女人至少总有七八个，你为什么偏偏盯上了她？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_fang_yu_fei",
      "text": "因为她不睬我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "方玉飞",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你难道想所有的女人一看见你，就跪下来吻你的脚？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_fang_yu_fei",
      "text": "她至少应该看我一眼的，我至少不是个很难看的男人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "方玉飞",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你就算要看她，最好也离她远一点！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_fang_yu_fei",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "方玉飞",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这女人是个冰山，你若想去动她，小心手上生冻疮！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "方玉飞",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你真的要去爬冰山？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_fang_yu_fei",
      "text": "我不怕得冻疮！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "方玉飞",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是你总得小心，冰山上很滑，你小心摔下来！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_fang_yu_fei",
      "text": "你摔过几次？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "方玉飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "从这座冰山上摔下来，最多只能摔一次，因为一次已经可以把人摔死。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你跟着我干什么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "text": "我害你输了钱，心里也很难受，所以……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "所以你想赔偿我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你想怎么样赔偿？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "text": "我知道城里有个吃宵夜的地方，是通宵开着的，酒菜都很不错，现在夜已很深，你一定也有点饿了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这么样不好，我有更好的法子。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "text": "什么法子？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你过来，我告诉你。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "像你这种男人我见得多了，就像是苍蝇臭虫，我一看见就想吐！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不是苍蝇，也不叫臭虫，我姓陆，叫陆小凤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我姓冷，冷若霜。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "text": "刚才那四个人你认得？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "text": "他们为什么要欺负你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我的家就住在永乐巷，靠左边第一栋屋子！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "text": "永乐巷在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "刚才我们已经走过了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "text": "可是你……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我没有叫车子停下来，因为我今天晚上不想回家去！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "今天晚上我一直都在输，我想换个地方，换换手气！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你知不知道这里还有个金钩赌坊？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "text": "那地方很秘密？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你是从外地来的，当然不会知道！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "今天晚上你有没有别的事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你想不想我带你到那里去看看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "text": "想！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是我答应过那里的主人，绝不带陌生人进去的，你若真的想去，那也得答应我一个条件！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "让我把你的眼睛蒙起来，而且答应我绝不偷看！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "text": "我答应！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "text": "你最好用厚一点的布来蒙我的眼睛，有时候我的眼睛会透视。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你慢慢的走，跟着我走，我保证这地方绝不会让你失望的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "到了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谢天谢地！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ruo_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "冷若霜",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你先在这里站着，我去找这里的主人来！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "冷姑娘，冷若霜！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好功夫！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_bu_tou",
      "speaker_name": "杨捕头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你……你敢拒捕？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 507
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yang_bu_tou",
      "text": "拒捕？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yang_bu_tou",
      "text": "你是从衙门里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "有人",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这位就是府衙里的杨捕头，你敢拒捕，就是叛逆！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yang_bu_tou",
      "text": "你们是来拿我的？我犯了什么罪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_bu_tou",
      "speaker_name": "杨捕头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "光棍眼里不揉沙子，真人面前不说假话，人证物证俱在，你还装什么蒜？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 521
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yang_bu_tou",
      "text": "人证在哪里？物证在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "有人",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "就是他！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 527,
      "line_end": 527
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "有人",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "昨天晚上，就是这个脸上长着四条眉毛的恶贼，强奸了我老婆！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_bu_tou",
      "speaker_name": "杨捕头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你昨晚上，一夜之间做了八件大案！这就是人证。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "官差",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这都是从你屋里搜出来的，这就是物证。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yang_bu_tou",
      "text": "我若真的偷了人家东西，难道会就这么光明正大的摆在屋子里，难道我看来真的这么笨？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 543
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_bu_tou",
      "speaker_name": "杨捕头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "听你的口气，难道还有人冒险去抢了这么多东西来送给你？难道你是他的亲老子么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老人",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "杀人越货，强奸民妇，全都不要紧，只要我们不管这件事，还是一样可以逍遥法外。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 553
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "杀人越货，强奸民妇，全都不要紧？什么事才要紧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老人",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不管你做什么事都不要紧，但你却不该惹到我们身上来！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 565
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "你们是哪一方的神圣？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老人",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你不认得？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "不认得！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老人",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在你还是不认得？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "不认得！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老人",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在你认不认得？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "还是不认得！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老人",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你也认得出这是好功夫？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "现在我总算已知道你们是谁了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "但我却还是不知道，我有什么地方得罪了你们？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九天十地，诸神诸魔，俱入我门，唯命是从！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "三个老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九天十地，诸神之子，遇难遭劫，神魔俱泣。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 629
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "这个人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老人",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在已是个死人！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "他活着的时候呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九天十地，诸神之子，遇难遭劫，神魔俱泣。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 645
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "难道他是你们教主的儿子？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老人",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "哼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "难道他是死在我手上的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老人",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "杀人者死！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有人要抓我去归案，有人要我死，我只有一个人，怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 657
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老人",
      "listener": "char_yang_bu_tou",
      "text": "你一定要他去归案？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_bu_tou",
      "speaker_name": "杨捕头",
      "listener": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "不……不……不一定！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "这么样看来，好像我已非死不可。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 666,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老人",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "但是我也知道，你临死之前，必定还要拼一拼！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "一点也不错！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老人",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你这是班门弄斧！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 674,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你杀了诸神之子，纵然上天入地，也难逃一死。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 694,
      "line_end": 695
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_da_niu",
      "text": "来过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 794,
      "line_end": 794
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "既然来过，就该知道这地方的规矩！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 796,
      "line_end": 796
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xia_zi",
      "text": "赌场也有规矩？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 798,
      "line_end": 798
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不但有规矩，而且比衙门的规矩还大。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 800,
      "line_end": 800
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_niu",
      "speaker_name": "大牛",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不到天黑，就算天王老子来，我们也一样要请他出去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 804,
      "line_end": 805
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_da_niu",
      "text": "难道我进去看看都不行？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 808,
      "line_end": 808
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_niu",
      "speaker_name": "大牛",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不行！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 810,
      "line_end": 810
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_da_niu",
      "text": "我敢赌五百两银子，赌你一定没法子举起这石凳子来。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 812,
      "line_end": 813
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_da_niu",
      "text": "看样子这次是我输了，这五百两银子已经是你的！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 822,
      "line_end": 823
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在离天黑已不远，你到外面去转一转再回来，我可以替你找几个好脚，痛痛快快的赌一场！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 834,
      "line_end": 835
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xia_zi",
      "text": "我就在这里面转一转行不行？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 838,
      "line_end": 838
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_niu",
      "speaker_name": "大牛",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不行！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 840,
      "line_end": 840
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_da_niu",
      "text": "既然不到天黑，绝不开赌，你刚才为什么要跟我赌？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 842,
      "line_end": 843
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_niu",
      "speaker_name": "大牛",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我没有！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 846,
      "line_end": 846
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_da_niu",
      "text": "你若没有跟我赌，为什么收了我五百两银子？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 848,
      "line_end": 849
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这幅画是我们老板以前那位大舅子画的，简直画得比我还糟，那边有幅江南第一才子唐解元的山水，那才叫山水！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 888,
      "line_end": 889
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_niu",
      "speaker_name": "大牛",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我带你过去看看，你就知道这幅画简直是狗屁了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 892,
      "line_end": 893
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_da_niu",
      "text": "我宁可看狗屁！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 896,
      "line_end": 896
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_niu",
      "speaker_name": "大牛",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 898,
      "line_end": 898
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_da_niu",
      "text": "山水到处都可看见，狗屁却少见得很！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 900,
      "line_end": 900
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子鬼鬼祟祟，一看就不是好东西，留不得他！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 910,
      "line_end": 910
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_niu",
      "speaker_name": "大牛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对，咱们先请他出去，废了他一双手再说！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 912,
      "line_end": 912
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们说得不错，这幅画实在是狗屁！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 924,
      "line_end": 924
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "画虽然狗屁，真正的狗屁，看来还在后面哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 930,
      "line_end": 930
